{"tid":1275393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"喺愉景灣發緊夢嘅手足","createTime":"2019-07-01T19:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T20:31:48.000Z","uid":252321,"like":52,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ff119cb1ef98043b52936b79bb27c13d9741b2f4","tid":1275393,"uid":252321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:35:24.000Z","msg":"如果怕聽朝唔夠錢搭車出返市區，或者想聽朝七點後想喺愉景灣搵個地方沐浴更衣，如果信得過小弟嘅，請telegram 小弟：master_claw，聽朝會有人接濟你哋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n同埋聽過有人話碼頭附近有通宵村巴去馬灣，可以轉車出返葵芳青衣，但我唔知真假<br />\n<br />\n建議你哋最好聚堆一齊，喺愉景北廣場或愉景廣場附近逗留，咁就只需要搵一個人telegram 我<br />\n<br />\n同堆愉景灣好撚多蚊同蠓，如非必要，請遠離草叢，小心變蚊蠓放題"},{"pid":"7edaaf7caeb05ef89ddd75a7fed51ab32b7d0b17","tid":1275393,"uid":33495,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:36:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a5a24bf430325b8e3c7f379ec7cfcf2fef0519f","tid":1275393,"uid":241536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:37:48.000Z","msg":"b"},{"pid":"ac66e149da97add6eb2928458ea9742b32d2c3af","tid":1275393,"uid":254788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:38:32.000Z","msg":"Sor禁錯負皮<br />\n推"},{"pid":"9bf4313e163f08a5831b9d74c44dc1a0840d92ee","tid":1275393,"uid":801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:39:22.000Z","msg":"馬灣撚表示 有通宵車出青衣同葵芳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8110141aada25e1e2c60cf53fb48b054af9319c","tid":1275393,"uid":212509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:40:05.000Z","msg":"愉景有車返東涌同欣澳<br />\n去青衣荃灣那個係珀麗灣"},{"pid":"387a06aa4cdf5862dcc0c668fcca2bb1cf46dc3d","tid":1275393,"uid":252321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T19:41:28.000Z","msg":"愉景灣出欣澳/東涌巴士 十幾蚊<br />\n再轉狗鐵 （用唔到都會票）十幾至三十蚊走唔甩（睇你住邊）"},{"pid":"e8673c72ccdd8ff74a4dbca04250e025f2b3874e","tid":1275393,"uid":252321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a8110141a